    @InterfaceAudience.Private
 @InterfaceStability.Unstable
public class NodeTimelineCollectorManager
extends TimelineCollectorManager
    Class on the NodeManager side that manages adding and removing collectors and their lifecycle. Also instantiates the per-node collector webapp.
